🐳 2. Dockerized Microservices Project
What to build:
Split an app into 2–3 microservices (e.g., user service, product service)
DevOps focus:
Dockerize each service
Use Docker Compose for orchestration
Add Nginx as reverse proxy
Bonus:
Add Redis or MongoDB
Implement service communication (REST APIs)
👉 Skills gained: Containers, microservices, networking
